N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 159.1 - Scope of part

State Regulations

The purpose of this Part is to establish standards of
instructional quality for economic development skills training programs and
entrepreneurship support center training programs pursuant to sections
200
(3)
and
212
(3)(c)
of the Economic Development Law, as
added by section 17 of chapter 839 of the Laws of 1987. Notes
